## 9. Rollback Plan

### Trigger Conditions
- Auth failures  
- Broken core flows  
- 5xx errors  
- Env misconfiguration  

### Procedure
1. Pause testing  
2. Redeploy last stable version  
3. Restore DB if needed  
4. Re-run smoke tests  

---

